data.description: Welcome to this charming and updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Humble. This delightful property boasts a warm and inviting atmosphere with its warm would beams and new flooring, making it the perfect place to call home. This home has been thoughtfully updated throughout, ensuring modern comfort and convenience while maintaining its classic charm. Whether you're enjoying quiet evenings by the fireplace or entertaining guests in the spacious backyard, this property offers a warm and inviting haven you'll be proud to call your own. This beautiful home is in the perfect location just minutes from tons of dining and shopping, Deerbrook Mall, the George Bush Continental Airport, and quick & easy access to US-59.Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming residence your forever home.
